while ( development of the new feature ) {
  edit .dtx file
  run update.sh with pdflatex on the example file commented
  run the example file
}

uncomment the "pdflatex on the example" line
check the final .pdf file of the class
check the final .pdf file of the example

in the .dtx file:
update the version of the class
add a global \changes{} to specify the main changes of the new version (not linked to a specific macro, these changes have to be documented within the macro)
update the compilation environment you used for compiling the class in the Section "Introduction"